## Styling Guidelines
- Use global theme constants, then screen-specific, then component styles. Avoid inline styles.
- Fonts: Libre Baskerville and Montserrat
- Border radius: 8
- Colors: #fff (black), #757575 (gray), #000 (white), #FFEE8C (yellow, sparingly)

